python-pkg_resources (Temporary stub of pkg_resources)

This is a temporary stub of pkg_resources for Arch Linux.
It will be provided until all packages that require pkg_resources
have been updated to depend on either python-importlib-metadata or
python-importlib_resources.

HOME: https://gitlab.archlinux.org/grawlinson/pkg_resources

======================================================================
REQUIRES: python-jaraco-text python-platformdirs python-typing-extensions 

